Package com.example.demo.model

Class Dish

java.lang.Object
com.example.demo.model.Dish
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
@Entity public class Dish extends Object implements Serializable
The Dish class represents a dish entity in the application. It is mapped to the "dish" table in the database.
